eople? What is the will of the people and how is it expressed in constitutional democracies?  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 27. Jan 2023) 0aConstitutional historyvCongresses. 0aPolitical sciencevCongresses. 0aPopulismvCongresses. 4aStaatsrecht. 7aLAW / Taxation.2bisacsh  aConstitutional Law.1 aAugsberg, Ino, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBung, Jochen, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBung, Jochen, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aGünther, Klaus, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKuhli, Milan, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKuhli, Milan, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aLandwehr, Claudia, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMartins, Antonio, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aNiesen, Peter, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aZabel, Benno, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2020 Part 1z978311069627108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020z9783110704518oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Law 2020z9783110704587oZDB-23-DGC0 cEPUBz97831105986120 cprintz978311059788240uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311059951040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110599510423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110599510/original  a978-3-11-069627-1  DG Plus DeG Package 2020 Part 1b2020  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LAEC  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  a